/**
 * @defgroup osal_file_api osal_file API
 * @ingroup osal_family_group
 *
 * @brief Low-level OSAL file abstraction.
 *
 * @details
 * The `osal_file` module provides portable low-level file primitives through
 * the OS abstraction layer.
 *
 * It is responsible for file-level operations only, and is not intended to
 * act as a runtime `stream` adapter.
 */
